## Prompt
Close prompt|Escape / Ctrl-c
Backward a word|Alt-b / Ctrl-Left
Backward a char|Ctrl-b / Left
Forward a word|Alt-f / Ctrl-Right
Forward a char|Ctrl-f / Right
Move to prompt end|Ctrl-e / End
Move to prompt start|Ctrl-a / Home
Delete previous word|Ctrl-w / Alt-Backspace
Delete next word|Alt-d / Ctrl-Delete
Delete to start of line|Ctrl-u
Delete to end of line|Ctrl-k
Delete previous char|Ctrl-h / Backspace
Delete next char|Ctrl-d / Delete
Insert word under doc cursor|Ctrl-r Ctrl-w
Select previous history|Up / Ctrl-p
Select next history|Down / Ctrl-n
Insert register content|Ctrl-r <char>
Select next completion item|Tab
Select previous completion item|Shift-Tab
Open selected|Enter
